log
@moved from top-level to src/other/.
@
text
@'\"
'\" Copyright (c) 1998-2000 by Scriptics Corporation.
'\" All rights reserved.
'\" 
'\" RCS: @@(#) $Id: packagens.n,v 1.3 2004/03/04 19:46:56 morrison Exp $
